  "instructions": [
    "heat coconut oil in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "add chopped onion and sauté until softened, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "add minced garlic and sauté for another minute.",
    "add diced chili pepper and sauté for another minute.",
    "add dashi powder, coriander powder, cumin powder, turmeric powder, salt, and black pepper. stir well to combine.",
    "add passata and stir well to combine.",
    "bring the mixture to a simmer and let cook for 10-12 minutes, or until the sauce has thickened slightly.",
    "add tofu cubes and stir well to combine.",
    "reduce heat to low and let cook for another 5 minutes, or until the tofu is cooked through.",
    "serve hot over rice or with roti."
  ],
